Problem Link:https://www.hackerrank.com/contests/simply-sql/challenges/the-pads

Solution: 

Solution:
(select concat(Name ,"(" , lefT(Occupation,1) , ")") as Nm from Occupations) 
union 
(SELECT CONCAT("There are a total of ", COUNT(Occupation), 
                                concat(" ", lower(occupation), "s.")) as Nm
                                FROM OCCUPATIONS 
                                GROUP BY Occupation ORDER BY count(OCCUPATION), occupation)
 order by Nm;

